text: Matthias Minder (born 3 February 1993) is a Swiss professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Swiss club Neuchâtel Xamax. ==Club career== A youth product of Winterthur, Minder transferred to Neuchâtel Xamax 1 May 2018. Minder made his professional debut with Xamax in a 3-1 Swiss Cup loss to FC Lugano on 31 October 2018. ==References== ==External links== * * Xamax Profile Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:People from Winterthur Category:Swiss footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Swiss Super League players Category:Swiss Challenge League players Category:Neuchâtel Xamax FCS players Category:FC Winterthur players
